'''Tamesgida n el-Aqṣa''' (s [[Taɛrabt|tserɣint]]: ''المسجد الأقصى'' neɣ ''الجامع القبلي'') d [[Tamesgida|tamesgida]] tameqrant yakk di tama n [[uṛacalim|Uṛacalim]], akken i iga d amur seg [[adrar n ufakan|wedrar n ufakan]] (maca mači akk s timmad-is). el-Aqṣa d tamsukt yettwallsen, d nnig-s tella yiwet n [[Takerbust|tkerbust]] n weldun, yezga-d s anẓul n wedrar n ufakan.

Yebnat-id Uxalifa [[Ɛumar Ibn Lxeṭṭab]] ass mi yenbez tamdint n Uṛcalim deg useggas n [[636]], dɣa d el-Aqṣa i d amẓalla (adeg n [[taẓallit|tẓallit]]) agejdan anda i d-temsegrawen imẓulla s deffir n [[imam|yimam]] deg tẓallit n [[Lǧumuɛa]] deg tmesgida n el-Aqṣa.<ref>[http://emasjid.net/masajid/alaqsa/p02_02.htm Tamesgida taliktrunt: Tamesgida n el-Aqṣa.] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170511091442/http://www.emasjid.net/masajid/alaqsa/p02_02.htm |date=11 mayyu 2017}}</ref> 

Llan waṭas n medden ttɣiken d akken Tamesgida n el-Aqṣa d tamesgida-nni yebnan kan s anẓul n [[Takerbust n weẓru|tkerbust n weẓru]], win deg wanda i tẓallan degs yirgazen semmus n tẓalliyin tura. Maca deg tidet, tamesgida n el-Aqṣa d ayen yellan yakk s agensu n weɣrab n tmesgida ula ma d isaragen-nni i s-izzin. Dɣa tajumma-ines s umata tga azal n 144000 m².<ref>[http://www.aqsaonline.org/news.aspx?id=180 di tmesgida n el-Aqṣa ] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822175611/http://www.aqsaonline.org/news.aspx?id=180 |date=22 ɣuct 2017}}</ref>

